{lang-eng}Mana devuni pattana mandaayana parishudda
Parvatha mandu yehovaa goppa vaadunu
Bahu keerta neeyudai yunnaadu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Uttara dikkuna maharaaju pattanamaina siyonu
Parvathamu unnathamai andamugaa sarva bhoomiki
Santoshamitchu chunnadi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Daani nagarulalo devudaashrayamugaa
Pratyakshambagu chunnaadu raaju lekomugaa koodi
Aashcharya padi brama padi thwaragaa velliri{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Achchata vaarala vanakunu prasavinchu stree vedana
Pattenu thoorpu gaalini repi tharsheeshu odala
Pagulagottu chunnaavu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sainyamu ladhipathi Yehovaa devuni pattanamu nandu
Manamu vini natti reethigaa jaruguta
Manmu choochitimi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Mana devudu nityamugaa daanini stiroparachi
Yunnaadu devaa nee aalaya manduna nee
Krupanu dhyaninchitimi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Devaa nee naamamu entha goppado nee
Satkeertiyunu bhoo dinganthamula varaku
Antha goppadai yunnadi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Ee devudu sadaakaalamu manaku devudai
Yunnaadu manala nadipinchunu marana
Paryanthamu Halleluya aamen{/lang-eng}
